{"tid":1407713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙有野想同各位講D野","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:56.000Z","uid":260616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"62eec3268315f8ab851839c93f9179691d3a1c54","tid":1407713,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢，黃大仙同我講，叫人去黃大仙求簽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃大仙</span></span>是一個好L正的地方<br />\n第一，去九西同荃葵青都要經龍翔道，獅子山其中一個入口都係要由龍翔轉入去<br />\n九東同港島東要去獅隧都要龍翔入去，所以是好好好好好好好<span style=\"color: red;\">重要</span>～～&middot;<br />\n<br />\n第二，龍翔道附近好多市民居住的地方，如果班狗射催淚彈，打人，開槍，有好多市民都會受到影響，同埋睇L住班狗，知道班狗有幾衰，到時民意會好容易企我地呢邊。<br />\n<br />\n第三，黃大仙附近的地至複雜，有好多位卑義士走 or 轉場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhRi7tm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhRi7tm.png&h=62d953f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以走去慈雲山，樂富，鑽石山，或者求簽！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家＋油！"},{"pid":"12b10ecc1b0c4fa439a267fd178afb4e7d930105","tid":1407713,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a8abb722bd365042e8fc9f95b8462aad0de19459","tid":1407713,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"e1403a3f7f942660548ac45c82765108bec5dcf9","tid":1407713,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"4913abc69cdb0c5bff1bb1fa55611dbb36682ec2","tid":1407713,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c162433615f28fb01ed32de96a727c7ace9262bb","tid":1407713,"uid":41290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d01e60d902ee9f31e861311c5821395758d1c50","tid":1407713,"uid":281547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T17:30:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\